title: Readout of President Joe Biden’s Meeting with President Gitanas Nausėda of Lithuania | The White House
content: President Joe Biden met with President Gitanas Nausėda of Lithuania in Vilnius on July 11, 2023. President Biden thanked President Nausėda for Lithuania’s hospitality in hosting the 2023 NATO Summit. He emphasized the ironclad U.S. commitment to NATO security, demonstrated through persistent, consecutive rotations of U.S. military personnel in Lithuania. The leaders discussed their ongoing commitment to Ukraine’s security and imposing costs on Russia for its aggression for as long as necessary.###
